-- SAP Co-CEO Sees More Customers by 2015, `Optimistic' on Growth, FT Reports
-- Ben Martin
-- 2010-08-01T21:13:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-01/sap-co-ceo-sees-more-customers-by-2015-optimistic-on-growth-ft-reports.html

          
          
             SAP AG  Co-Chief Executive Officer
 Bill McDermott  said the company will have “significantly more
customers by 2015” and that he is “very optimistic” about its
prospects for growth, the Financial Times reported, citing an
interview.  
 McDermott said it’s possible the company may surpass its
full-year guidance for software and related service revenues,
the newspaper also reported.  
